request.description:
/userId

Set the user roles based on his id.

Pass a list of objects containing the roles for the user:

> \[  
{  
"value": "APPROVER",  
"label": "Approver",  
"disabled": false  
},  
{  
"value": "CONTROLLER",  
"label": "Controller",  
"disabled": false  
},  
{  
"value": "ADDRESS_MANAGER",  
"label": "Address Manager",  
"disabled": false  
}  
\]
